  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are a victim</strong> of circumstances in a winter forest, where every step echoes in the silence. Will you be able to find the way out, or will you remain in this silent nightmare forever?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/6a6fdddd0781c92d1d3e6dfc63a30cfa.poster.avif?t=1754592279\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/6a6fdddd0781c92d1d3e6dfc63a30cfa.webm?t=1754592279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/6a6fdddd0781c92d1d3e6dfc63a30cfa.mp4?t=1754592279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What awaits you there.. or who?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KRAMPEN</strong> is a digital horror-adventure game in which you will immerse yourself in a winter forest and help a lost soul regain a piece of itself. Uncover all the secrets that go beyond the gaming experience and discover the truth about the main character!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/0502e9c26cfdd80a9db4df16dcbec78c.poster.avif?t=1754592279\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/0502e9c26cfdd80a9db4df16dcbec78c.webm?t=1754592279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/0502e9c26cfdd80a9db4df16dcbec78c.mp4?t=1754592279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The winter forest is deeper than it seems..</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >..it remembers all your deeds. The further you go into the forest, the more <span class=\"bb_strike\">firewood</span> there is. You will encounter a talking bush, a drunken stone, a psychologist fish, and many others. What secrets does the mysterious winter forest hold, once a witness to brutal violence, leaving its marks on the pristine canvas of winter?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/0d37c2aaded87f3608cbd8c76bb7988b.poster.avif?t=1754592279\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/0d37c2aaded87f3608cbd8c76bb7988b.webm?t=1754592279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/0d37c2aaded87f3608cbd8c76bb7988b.mp4?t=1754592279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This place is filled with a dark atmosphere of confusion and anxiety..</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
